data.description: Discover your serene retreat in this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom stucco home nestled in the heart of Kingsland! Set on an expansive 1/3-acre lot in the coveted Royal Acres subdivision, this residence boasts undeniable curb appeal with lush grass and tropical landscaping. A wooden privacy fence encloses the spacious yard, creating a haven for relaxation and entertainment.    Hidden amidst the greenery, you'll find dedicated spaces for leisure, including a delightful treehouse for the little ones, a quaint chicken coop, and an ideal spot for cultivating your garden oasis. Outdoor amenities extend to a pergola with a secluded outdoor bathtub accessible through French doors in the primary suiteaan exquisite touch of luxury. A multipurpose shed tucked in the corner provides versatility, perfect for a private gym, office, or creative haven.    Step inside to discover laminate flooring gracing the bedrooms and living areas, creating a seamless and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances, sleek concrete countertops, and stylish tile flooring, combining both functionality and aesthetics. Each bedroom offers ample storage, with the primary suite's walk-in closet unveiling a charming secret room.    This inviting abode comes complete with all appliances, including the washer and dryer, ensuring a turnkey transition into your new oasis. Don't miss the chance to call this haven homeawhere comfort, style, and outdoor bliss converge
